OL,3,CNigel Farage declares #270,000 payment
OL,4,Cfor promoting gold bullion
OL,6,FNigel Farage has declared his largest
OL,7,Fsingle payment yet for work outside
OL,8,Fhis role as an MP, after earning
OL,9,F#270,000 for promoting gold bullion.
OL,11,FThe Reform UK leader declared the
OL,12,Fpayment from Direct Bullion in his
OL,13,Flatest register of financial interests.
OL,15,FThe #270,000 payment was for an
OL,16,Festimate of up to four hours work "per
OL,17,Fmonth over the course of a three month
OL,18,Fperiod", which equates to Farage
OL,19,Fearning more than #22,000 an hour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
