OL,3,CNigel Farage declares #270,000 payment
OL,4,Cfor promoting gold bullion
OL,6,FFarage works as a brand ambassador for
OL,7,Fthe company and has registered several
OL,8,Fother payments from Direct Bullion in
OL,9,Fthe past.
OL,11,FA spokesman for Farage said: "As has
OL,12,Fpreviously been reported and declared,
OL,13,FNigel Farage is a brand ambassador for
OL,14,FDirect Bullion."
OL,16,FAccording to the Reform leader's
OL,17,Flatest register entry, he also earned
OL,18,F#18,402 for an estimated six hours of
OL,19,Fpresenting on GB News.
