OL,3,CNigel Farage declares #270,000 payment
OL,4,Cfor promoting gold bullion
OL,6,FWhen Sir Keir Starmer was elected as
OL,7,Fprime minister in 2024, he created a
OL,8,Frule where Labour MPs could not have
OL,9,Fsecond jobs but this does not apply to
OL,10,Fother parties.
OL,12,FFarage has continued to take public
OL,13,Fspeaking jobs, appearances on the site
OL,14,FCameo and sponsorship deals with
OL,15,FDirect Bullion.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
