OL,3,CNigel Farage declares #270,000 payment
OL,4,Cfor promoting gold bullion
OL,6,FThis comes at a time where Farage
OL,7,Fcontinues to face questions about a
OL,8,F#5m gift he received from Thai-based
OL,9,Fbillionaire Christopher Harborne.
OL,11,FFarage has continually said that he
OL,12,Fdid not need to declare the gift, as
OL,13,Fit was given before he announced his
OL,14,Fintention to stand for Parliament in
OL,15,F2024 and that it was not related to
OL,16,Fpolitics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
