PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782895707
OL,3,CNigel Farage declares #270,000 payment
OL,4,Cfor promoting gold bullion
OL,6,FThe code of conduct for declarations
OL,7,Ffor MPs state that "new Members must
OL,8,Fregister all their current financial
OL,9,Finterests, and any registrable
OL,10,Fbenefits received in the 12 months
OL,11,Fbefore their election"
OL,13,FThe Clacton MP has given a variety of
OL,14,Fexplanations for the gift, including
OL,15,Fthat it was to pay for his personal
OL,16,Fsecurity, and that it was a "reward"
OL,17,Ffor campaigning for Brexit throughout
OL,18,Fhis political career and insists that
OL,19,Fit does not need declaring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
