OL,3,CNigel Farage declares #270,000 payment
OL,4,Cfor promoting gold bullion
OL,6,FFarage has recently said the gift was
OL,7,Fa "wholly private matter" and told ITV
OL,8,Fthat "no one cares" but was unclear as
OL,9,Fto whether he has actually spent it
OL,10,Fyet.
OL,12,FParliament's standards commissioner is
OL,13,Fcurrently investigating whether the
OL,14,Fgift should have been registered.
